{"id":201439,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/数百特警围攻陆丰乌坎村-多图/","date":"2011-12-12T00:32:12Z","modified":"2011-12-28T23:57:35Z","title":"数百特警围攻陆丰乌坎村 (多图)","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>2011</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>12</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>11</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日早上四时半，当局出动数百特警和多辆防暴车向陆丰乌坎村进攻，村口的放哨村民发觉后，立刻敲响铜锣，全体村民拿起棍棒集结村口阻档，特警不敢强攻，双方对峙至上午六时。</span><br />\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><br />\n<span lang=\"EN-US\">警方假意撤退，村民以为警方已退，试图在村口堆放树木拦路，这时警方突然调头攻击，向村民施放数十个催泪弹，引起草地起火，并发射水炮，村民顽抗，双方混战近一小时，早上七时许特警缓缓退去。</span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\">虽然较早前村民曾向外求援，但因所有进村路口已被警察堵住，连上网的宽带也封锁，所以外间无法施以援手。</span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div>\n<strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">村民在网上<span>呼吁</span>在外村民<span>回</span><span>乡抗敌：</span></span></strong></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<br />\n<span lang=\"EN-US\">特级通告</span><span>..</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">全部陆丰的人民百姓们</span><span>&#8230;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">请速回陆丰</span><span>.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">我们不怕</span><span>.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">誓言和鬼子抗战到底</span><span>..</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">保护家乡</span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span lang=\"EN-US\">各位兄弟姐妹，我们的家乡就要被陆丰政府一手遮天了，如果心有家乡的请快回来吧！刚才鬼子已经进村强抓村民了！我们要跟乌砍共存亡</span><span>&#8230;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">打鬼子</span><span></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_lwbgrtWmaY/TuR-zop9JPI/AAAAAAAAF9o/Y3JjIyxC4so/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_lwbgrtWmaY/TuR-zop9JPI/AAAAAAAAF9o/Y3JjIyxC4so/s640/1.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-6X7z3jzMxf0/TuR-3tFF5mI/AAAAAAAAF-I/e74ZqNXcDiE/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-6X7z3jzMxf0/TuR-3tFF5mI/AAAAAAAAF-I/e74ZqNXcDiE/s640/4.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"htt